column5: Has anyone stayed at Kingfisher Lodge or fished Wabaskang Lake in Perrault Falls, Ont.? I was talking to them at the Sportsmans show and it seems like a good deal, any opinions?
Planning my first trip there this July. Do a search of this site for "Wabaskang lake" there is a current thread that talks about Wabaskang and some of the lodges on the lake.
